        "answer": "Caleb Consulting Ltd Uganda's official website is https://calebconsultancyservices.com. It offers financial and management consulting services. The firm is based in Kampala, Uganda.\nCaleb Consulting Ltd Uganda is a management consultancy firm offering services like risk assurance and financial advisory. It was founded in 2012 and has 2-10 employees. The firm provides remote consulting services globally.\nCaleb Consulting Ltd Uganda is a business consultancy founded in 2012, offering services in governance, risk, compliance, and HR outsourcing. It has not raised any funding and operates with 2-10 employees.\nCaleb Consulting Ltd Uganda is a management consultancy firm offering various services globally. The CEO is Dr. Bamidele Olalekan Oseni, with extensive experience in banking and consultancy. Wellfound is a platform for startup job searches.\nCaleb Consulting Ltd Uganda is a management consultancy firm offering financial and risk advisory services, headquartered in Kampala, Uganda. The CEO is Dr. Bamidele Olalekan Oseni, with over 25 years of experience in banking and consultancy. The firm provides remote services globally.",
